node.text: I cleaned my room today & laid on my bed to relax after. 👀 looked up to find a thick layer of dust on my fan. Let this be a reminder to clean yooo fan, friends.✌🏼🤢

node.text: I re-potted my Marble Queen #pothos today & she’s looking happier than ever! I’m always recommending pothos or a heartleaf philodendron to beginners because of how easy they are to care for. AND their leafy vines add so much beauty to any space. 😍

node.text: Remember that one time I said I’d never leave an air fryer out on the counter? Well I take it back. You were right! We use this thing almost daily! I was just worried about counter space since our kitchen is small but we are making it work. 🙌🏼
The Valley Carpenter Bee, also known as the Teddy Bear Bee. 🥰🐻🐝 He visits my garden daily & I thought he deserved a permanent spot on my feed. #teddybearbee #beeslife #california
